lass="_ _6"></span>其实，<span class="_ _a"></span>生活就是这样，<span class="_ _6"></span>苦乐一直在此起彼伏，<span class="_ _a"></span>如</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y81 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">果你没有任何信仰，<span class="_ _5"></span>对此没有做过准备，<span class="_ _5"></span>可能觉得痛苦是突</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y82 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">如其来，一遇到挫折就怨天尤人。 </div><div class="t m0 xc h4 y8d ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">但如果你从小学习过一些佛教思想，<span class="_ _5"></span>至少也会知道：<span class="_ _5"></span>这</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y66 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls10 ws0">种现象并不是由于今生太倒霉，而是<span class="ls11">跟自己前世的业力有</span></div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y85 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">关。<span class="_ _6"></span>有了这样的认识，<span class="_ _6"></span>很多事情就会想得开，<span class="_ _6"></span>发生什么也比</div><div class="t m0 x9 h4 y86 ffb fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">较容易接受。 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.500000,0.000000,0.000000,1.500000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
